headline: Baker Hughes : PETRONAS Collaborate to Meet Asia-Pacific Region’s Energy Expansion…
summary: Memorandum of Understanding aims to identify technologies within Baker Hughes' and PETRONAS' broad portfolio of solutions that are complementary and have potential to support Asia's energy expansion...
